@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_broklu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    tmp = (tmp / ((v0 + 0.35 * tmp + 0.74) + 0.82))
    tmp = (tmp + ((v2 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.22) + (v1 + 0.91 / v2 + 0.96)))
    v2 = v2
    v0 = (0.31 / ((v1 + 0.70 / tmp + 0.46) - (v1 + 0.26 - v0 + 0.71)))
    v1 = (0.93 * wp.abs((tmp + 0.81 / v0 + 0.93)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.72)) - v0)
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
